<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:12:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>2024 年达沃斯：Bajaj Finserv 首席执行官表示，印度正处于 FDI 洪流的风口浪尖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-cusp-fdi-flood-bajaj-finserv-chair-says-davos-2024-01-15/</link><description>作者：A Galani 和 Anthony Slodkowski</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-cusp-fdi-flood-bajaj-finserv-chair-says-davos-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>格鲁吉亚执政党领导人访华推动深化双边关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/georgias-ruling-party-leader-visits-china-push-deeper-ties-2024-01-15/</link><description>据格鲁吉亚媒体报道，格鲁吉亚执政党领导人周一开始对中国进行为期六天的访问，这个欧盟候选成员国寻求深化与北京的关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/georgias-ruling-party-leader-visits-china-push-deeper-ties-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：玩具制造商从中国转移并非易事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/toy-manufacturers-shift-china-is-no-childs-play-2024-01-15/</link><description>正在努力应对中国成本飙升的玩具制造商在将生产转移到其他更便宜的中心时没有找到简单的选择。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 13:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/toy-manufacturers-shift-china-is-no-childs-play-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国与瑞士签署扩大贸易宣言</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-switzerland-sign-declaration-with-view-expanding-trade-2024-01-15/</link><description>瑞士政府表示，李强总理会见瑞士总统后，中国和瑞士周一签署了一份联合声明，同意深化合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 13:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-switzerland-sign-declaration-with-view-expanding-trade-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>反对派拖延后，改革派阿雷瓦洛就任危地马拉总统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/reformist-arevalo-assumes-guatemalan-presidency-after-opposition-delays-2024-01-15/</link><description>反腐败斗士贝尔纳多·阿雷瓦洛周一早些时候就任危地马拉总统，反对派议员在最后一刻试图削弱他的权威，导致就职典礼陷入混乱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/reformist-arevalo-assumes-guatemalan-presidency-after-opposition-delays-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：胡塞武装袭击暴露了中国在红海的商业利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-expose-chinas-commercial-stakes-red-sea-2024-01-15/</link><description>中国呼吁停止对红海民用船只的袭击，这种袭击极大地扩大了哈马斯与以色列的冲突，并使北京在苏伊士运河沿岸的商业利益面临风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-expose-chinas-commercial-stakes-red-sea-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜黑客与犯罪分子在东南亚共享洗钱网络 - 联合国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-hackers-criminals-share-money-laundering-networks-southeast-asia-un-2024-01-15/</link><description>根据周一发布的联合国报告，朝鲜黑客正在与东南亚的欺诈者和毒贩共享洗钱和地下银行网络，赌场和加密货币交易所成为有组织犯罪的主要场所。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-hackers-criminals-share-money-laundering-networks-southeast-asia-un-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：为什么马尔代夫希望印度军队撤离</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-maldives-wants-indian-troops-out-2024-01-15/</link><description>马尔代夫新任总统于 3 月 15 日星期日为邻国印度设定了从这个印度洋群岛小国撤军的最后期限。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-maldives-wants-indian-troops-out-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国经济增速预计将放缓至4.6%，引发政策制定者的关注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-growth-seen-slowing-46-2024-raising-heat-policymakers-2024-01-15/</link><description>路透调查显示，中国经济增长可能在2024年放缓至4.6%，并在2025年进一步降温至4.5%，在通货紧缩压力和房地产严重下滑的情况下，政策制定者推出更多刺激措施的压力加大。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-growth-seen-slowing-46-2024-raising-heat-policymakers-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>随着竞争加剧，苹果在中国以罕见的折扣出售 iPhone 15</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-15-rare-discount-china-competition-intensifies-2024-01-15/</link><description>由于全球最大智能手机市场的竞争压力日益加大，苹果公司在中国为其 iPhone 提供罕见的折扣，零售价降低了 500 元人民币（合 70 美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:58:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-15-rare-discount-china-competition-intensifies-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军方将在南海开发岛屿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-develop-islands-south-china-sea-military-chief-2024-01-15/</link><description>马尼拉军事参谋长罗密欧·布劳纳周一对记者表示，菲律宾将在南海开发岛屿，这些岛屿被认为是其领土的一部分，以使这些岛屿更适合军队居住。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:50:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-develop-islands-south-china-sea-military-chief-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>台湾失去盟友瑙鲁，指责中国的选举后策略</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-loses-first-ally-post-election-nauru-goes-over-china-2024-01-15/</link><description>周一，就在台湾选出新总统几天后，台湾失去了仅存的几个外交盟友瑙鲁之一，并指责中国试图向台湾施压，同时又重申了台湾人走向世界的意愿。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:18:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-loses-first-ally-post-election-nauru-goes-over-china-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>日本企业预计中国2024年经济前景依然严峻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japanese-firms-expect-chinas-2024-economic-prospects-remain-grim-2024-01-15/</link><description>中国日本商工会议所周一发布的一份报告显示，在华日本企业预计今年世界第二大经济体的经济前景依然严峻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japanese-firms-expect-chinas-2024-economic-prospects-remain-grim-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>阿拉斯加事故后，波音 737 MAX 向中国的交付面临新的延误 - 华尔街日报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-737-max-deliveries-china-face-fresh-delay-after-alaska-incident-wsj-2024-01-15/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周日报道，本月阿拉斯加航空 MAX 9 飞机的一块面板在空中爆炸后，波音公司在恢复向中国交付 737 MAX 飞机方面面临着新的延迟。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-737-max-deliveries-china-face-fresh-delay-after-alaska-incident-wsj-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：朝鲜为什么要测试高超音速导弹以及它们是如何工作的？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-is-north-korea-testing-hypersonic-missiles-how-do-they-work-2024-01-15/</link><description>朝鲜周一表示，在对难以探测和拦截的下一代远程火箭的激烈竞争中，它已经测试了一种新型中程固体燃料高超音速导弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-is-north-korea-testing-hypersonic-missiles-how-do-they-work-2024-01-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>